{"tid":271482,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 Iphone 自動熄機之後開唔返","createTime":"2017-06-05T06:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T10:11:59.000Z","uid":5807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44241869aa42cd80d97a0d981a5cdb85c69120c3","tid":271482,"uid":5807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:20:40.000Z","msg":"岩岩用用下佢自己熄左機 (無留意幾多%, 因為佢冇彈low battery,冇諗過佢會自己熄)<br />\n<br />\n之後佢出左叫我叉電畫面，我插左USB佢就咁show 電池同一小格紅色電量，冇平時叉緊電個閃電logo，紅色電量果度又冇郁郁下表示佢叉緊<br />\n之後我再用原裝頭同線叉，情況都一樣<br />\n<br />\n我舊電係咪已經死左，有冇方法打救佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果真係要換電又想keep番入面D野，去apple搞係咪冇可能做到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bf0f086101d0d02c127cd15984ad61ffd1e0f8","tid":271482,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"換電 資料唔會無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4626c6f33342c62dbbcc4051dfb8ff7623b0fe","tid":271482,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"你叉左幾耐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd17720db964b08d14534f540690f1b64d554a9","tid":271482,"uid":79799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:26:43.000Z","msg":"你有無試下同時撳住粒bottom同開關？"},{"pid":"8a5afdf2e15ee913725b49f8ee68453c853b2d59","tid":271482,"uid":5807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換電 資料唔會無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\napple 唔係會同你reset部機先俾返你? 一陣放工去問下先"},{"pid":"90cee44aecb1ef9f098fabc3cedcefa84557d191","tid":271482,"uid":5807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"