://support.apple.com/zh-tw/ht201412</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/144609_923381855d1ff57c95fe50842f556650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F144609_923381855d1ff57c95fe50842f556650.jpg&h=257f4410&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/144612_f4f9842d9078879e3384db5e8ab42669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F144612_f4f9842d9078879e3384db5e8ab42669.jpg&h=797e5ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你依家係邊個畫面先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n插左線叉電果陣係左，冇插既時候係右<br />\n<br />\n照apple條link睇我係咪應該由佢試下叉多幾個鐘，唔得先再算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用原裝火牛叉一個鐘<br />\n唔好搞佢<br />\n一個鐘之後睇下佢會唔會自動着返"},{"pid":"182fb83684783b01181749ed0fe5c3e9ae38ea78","tid":271482,"uid":5807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/ht201412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fht201412&d=XNtAwD5yvMaNfXBIg6XGQk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=1ffd18d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/ht201412</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/144609_923381855d1ff57c95fe50842f556650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F144609_923381855d1ff57c95fe50842f556650.jpg&h=257f4410&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/144612_f4f9842d9078879e3384db5e8ab42669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F144612_f4f9842d9078879e3384db5e8ab42669.jpg&h=797e5ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你依家係邊個畫面先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n插左線叉電果陣係左，冇插既時候係右<br />\n<br />\n照apple